caption:
In our latest #HumansOfHOKA film, Thomas Panek shares his powerful journey through vision loss, rediscovering running and building a more inclusive path forward for the visually impaired community. 
By starting the world's first running guide dog program in 2015 ( @GuidingEyes ), Thomas proves that movement is for everyone. 

🔗🎥 Watch the full film at the link in bio.
